    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout that\u2019s best suited for someone after cheap wheels, a project, or a handy spare car. It\u2019s in rougher cosmetic shape and not a showroom example, but it still has plenty of character and could be a great value for the right buyer. If you\u2019re practical, know your way around cars, or just want something affordable with potential, this could be well worth a look. Priced fairly and offered by someone who\u2019d rather be upfront than oversell it.",
